Class InputDataManager

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.controller.EditorEventDataManager
oogasalad.editor.controller.InputDataManager
public class InputDataManager extends EditorEventDataManager
Manages the Input Event related data of a specific object. Implements EditorEventDataManager for methods pertaining to event, outcome, and condition lists and classes.
Author:
Jacob You
